{
  "stem": "4361.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was not necessarily the sequence of the way that-- I-- I forgot and I don't even want to remember, perhaps, anymore-- but these were the three colors.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And those flags were my father's flags.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I remember standing with him as we were watching the Hungarian cavalry, the Hussars, come in and the gendarmes with the plume helmet, the gendarmes.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my father-- I looked up at him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was a very tall man, a very handsome man and I adored him, clearly.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I looked up at him, and I saw tears streaming down his cheek 'because these are my people,' he said finally.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He never spoke Romanian, by the way, you know, until then, although it was Romania.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother spoke Romanian but not well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Of course, I spoke fluently.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And many years later, I remember telling my father-- and I wish I wouldn't have told him, perhaps.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember telling him, Daddy, remember how you wept?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Your Hungarians, look what they are doing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The first year, 1941, 1942, Hungarians didn't do much as far as my life-- as far as our life was concerned.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, the town-- you asked me earlier and I really didn't elaborate.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The town was sort of stratified, even within the Jewish communities.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, there were the well-to-do, the, you know, upper, middle, lower.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The poorest section was living in another side of the town.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were living in the not poor section.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so that life continued for a long time, except there were little things, little things.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I think before they got to the Jews, the Hungarians got to the Romanians, where there has always been and still is probably, a tremendous ethnic-- not conflict-- hatred between them.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
